msgstr "کاربس کا حساب لگائیں"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:81
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:81
